<*,*,it,*>: Secondo step
<*,*,*,*>:  Step 2
----
TTS
<*,*,*,*>: On a smooth surface, very gently form the dough into a ball. Wrap in plastic wrap and place in the fridge for one hour. Preheat oven to 350°F. Remove dough from the fridge, remove 1/4 of the dough, and roll the rest of the dough out with a rolling pin on a well floured surface until it’s 1/8″ thick. Almost finished!
